# vastai_cluster_member (Resource)

Manages membership of a machine in a Vast.ai cluster. Uses a composite ID format of `cluster_id/machine_id`. Both the cluster ID and machine ID are immutable after creation.

## Example Usage

{{ tffile "examples/resources/vastai_cluster_member/resource.tf" }}

{{ .SchemaMarkdown | trimspace }}

## Import

Cluster members can be imported using the composite ID `cluster_id/machine_id`:

```shell
terraform import vastai_cluster_member.example 123/456
```
